### Export Zip - Success Case (valid artifacts)
POST http://localhost:8010/export/zip
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "artifacts": [
    "Results/example_result.json",
    "benchmark_auto.csv"
  ]
}

### Export Zip - Empty artifacts list (should create empty zip)
POST http://localhost:8010/export/zip
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "artifacts": []
}

### Export Zip - Error Case (path traversal attempt)
POST http://localhost:8010/export/zip
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "artifacts": [
    "../../../etc/passwd"
  ]
}

### Export Zip - Error Case (file not found)
POST http://localhost:8010/export/zip
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "artifacts": [
    "nonexistent_file.json"
  ]
}
